from schnitzi mark schnitziu subject re atheist and hell atterlep cardinal ximenez write atheist believe that when they die they die forever a god who would condemn those who fail to believe in him to eternal death be unfair i do see what the problem be to christian hell be by definition eternal death exactly what atheist be expect when they die well i think that most christian believe that ymy conciousnes will somehow continue on after ymy death which contradict what most atheist myself include believe namely that ymy conciousnes be contain in ymy brain dy when ymy brain dy there no reason hell ha to be especially awful to most person eternal death be bad enough i fear the pain that often come with the proces of die but since i wo be around to worry about it i do fear eternal death literal interpreter of the bible will have a problem with thi view since the bible talk about the fire of hell and such thi be something i alway find confuse if all ymy nerve end die with ymy physical body why would flame hurt you how can one wail and gnash tooth with no lung and no tooth mark schnitziu schnitzi university of central florida 